text: Nim galluc <niþeweardne>, <gewyl> in þeorfum meolcum, <supe> gemet hat.
Nim <swegle> <æppel>, do in meolc, sele drincan.
Nim <nioþewerde> liðwyrt grene, wel in beore oþþe in þeorfum meolcum, supe þæt and drince swiþe.
Nim gesodene haran, ete wiþ þon.
Nim rudan, smeorowyrte, wel <in> ealoð sele drincan.
Nim henneægero þone geolocan and lybcorna þryttig and hwites sealtes godne dæl and wah meolo.
<Wyrttruman>, meng eal tosomne do in æges scylle, sete on gleda, do ealoð ænne sopan to <supe> swa hat.

Genim <grundeswelgian> and ellenrinde berynde utan, <wel> <þonne> <swiþe> in ealoð, asioh þurh clað, nim þonneviandxxxlybcorna, gnid smæle, do <wætes> hwon in, geot <innon> þone drenc, do butran on; dringe swa hat swa he hattost mæge and þonne stande and gange þær hine ne cæle.
